{"tid":1439572,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[低能連登仔］匯豐同太古都想批鬥","createTime":"2019-08-10T07:01:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T07:11:15.000Z","uid":21483,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"27c42968b742ece66b5b64888da8bc3e9e9a9b45","tid":1439572,"uid":21483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:01:34.000Z","msg":"喺啲低智連登仔眼中，非黑即白，一唔啱心意就割人地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但佢地唔知道好似匯豐同太古咁，有啲喺大到一定會俾政府影響到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而連登仔就忽略左佢地喺社會上努力爭取返佢地做到既公義。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n太古廣場果幾次幫手，連登仔已經拋諸腦後？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登仔係咪要割哂所有盟友，或者要啲良心企業賣盤走佬？到時香港得返全中資俾你全割先至滿意？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1474a97795a1be23dec3c50366e5e02c45223ce","tid":1439572,"uid":159916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:02:23.000Z","msg":"係，連登仔小氣過東方"},{"pid":"eebd7fd90c8fd52c82f96c99e45b3615982fe3fb","tid":1439572,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:02:32.000Z","msg":"連衛兵要立國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e9ef87dc8dc5a9d1b944aaf3afa22dc2d8badd9","tid":1439572,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:06:26.000Z","msg":"依種批鬥跟本係赤柬式政治純正嚟"},{"pid":"662693dd0a9b4e412b09ed0348ae6b8cb47a0ae2","tid":1439572,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:10:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><em><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無大台 只有自己代表到自己<br />\n不撤不散 各自努力<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span></ins></em></strong><br />\n唔好意思 阻你一陣<br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港人重點日程：<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>8月9-11日</strong>：機場和你飛&bull;萬人接機&bull;一連三日(1300)</span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>8月10日</strong>：銀髮族遞信「900警總」&gt;「1000律政司辦公室」&gt;「1100特首辦」<br />\n<strong>8月10日</strong>：守護孩子未來親子遊行（1030愛丁堡廣場）<br />\n<strong>8月10日</strong>：大埔遊行（1400大埔巴士總站）（反對通知書）</span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>8月11日</strong>：港島東遊行（1300維多利亞公園）<br />\n<strong>8月11日</strong>：深水埗遊行（1430楓樹街遊樂場）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">逢星期五，日擺買！減少家庭支出</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1c611c3c9d5371c16335193aecece799a8ca2337","tid":1439572,"uid":21483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:11:15.000Z","msg":"連登仔恃住有壓倒性既民意優勢，肆無忌憚咁樣割，唔會俾啲空間俾一啲會分是非黑白既企業<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地行錯一啲步伐，俾人捉左把柄或者有借口，到時俾政府或者大陸玩。玩到無利可圖既時候離開香港，到時連登仔就可以享受堅一言堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}